reviewText:
From what is shown on the cover is NOT what is inside. There is NOTHING whatsoever about tornados on any of the five disks.
This is a very mild documentary about some of the little known disasters that happens around the globe.
However, it still was interesting and will remain part of my growing dvd collection.
This is the second season of the series "Angry Planet."  George Kourounis travels the globe documenting extreme weather conditions and climates up close and personal.
